# Re-include test fixture: vault-mixed deliberately seeds a `private/` branch
# under the core test fixtures so the privacy pipeline's tripwire can be
# exercised end-to-end. Without this exception the broad `private` rule above
# silently drops new fixture additions (step 9 case (b) tripwire fixture lived
# only on disk, never in git, until this exception was added).
!packages/core/tests/fixtures/vault-mixed/private/
!packages/core/tests/fixtures/vault-mixed/private/**

# vendored font source archive — too large for GitHub's 50 MB recommendation
